com.realvnc.vncserver.android

Class VncCommandString

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.realvnc.vncserver.core.VncCommandStringBase
      • com.realvnc.vncserver.android.VncCommandString

  • public class VncCommandString
extends VncCommandStringBase
    Android implementation encapsulating a VNC Automotive command string. Note that in the past the terms "connection string" and "command string" have been used more-or-less interchangeably; both terms refer to the same thing.
